reviewText: I like these short stories to use in my Wednesday evening classes of 4 year olds.
Love the Bedbug Bible Gang.  Fun for the kids but the message is straight.
Entertaining and teaches good lessons. Very cute and clever.
great for kids.  I just wish there were more episodes on the disk.
great for kids.  I just wish there were more episodes on the disk.

Kids love the catchy songs and play along games.  I love the Bible lessons presented in a fun and engaging way. Several "less popular" stories are included in this series, beyond the standard David and Goliath and Noah's Ark stories that are in every kid's bible medium.
Awesome little cartoons for kids, I used this for Sunday School and the Kids loved it, I too enjoyed watching it.
